    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is recommended for those looking for a project car or a source of parts. The engine is currently suffering from significant oil leaks, and the transmission is slipping, indicating that major mechanical repairs will be necessary. Cosmetically, the exterior has visible rust and clear coat failure, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear with several missing trim pieces. It is sold strictly as-is.",
