    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is ideal as a project car or for parts. The engine currently runs but suffers from a persistent misfire and significant oil leaks, and the transmission shifts harshly between gears. On the exterior, there is noticeable rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and the clear coat is peeling extensively. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. It is being sold strictly as-is and will likely require towing.",
