    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she\u2019s a total beauty! This car is in incredible shape\u2014it honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this thing since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it\u2019s always spotless inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream, and you really won't find another one this clean. If you\u2019re looking for a total gem that\u2019s been loved and cared for, this is the one for you. Come take a look and see for yourself\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six engine. This unit is mechanically flawless, boasting a recent comprehensive VANOS overhaul and a precision valve adjustment to ensure peak volumetric efficiency across the powerband. The chassis is structurally sound with a proactively reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, eliminating the common fatigue points of this platform. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable Differential Lock. The exterior retains its original factory clear coat with no discernible swirl marks, while the Nappa leather interior remains supple with zero bolster wear. This is a pristine, turn-key example for the collector who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
